{"tid":1601273,"cid":5,"subCid":11,"title":"「小心撞鬼］數名黑布蒙面人進出政總　警反問為何查詢有關人士身份","createTime":"2019-09-29T03:45:09.000Z","updateTime":"2019-09-29T04:13:28.000Z","uid":58335,"like":8,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"3a9c01f5881faa6a592eed242ea71bd2a7591a46","tid":1601273,"uid":58335,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:45:09.000Z","msg":"有網民下午發起「全球反極權大遊行」，計劃由銅鑼灣遊行至金鐘政府總部。警方在政府總部一帶加強保安，記者觀察期間，有4名身穿深色衣服、戴太陽眼鏡，並以黑布蒙面的人員步出，看到記者後折返回政總閘內，又不斷指著記者。記者之後向在場身穿警察制服，並目睹蒙面人士進出的警員查問，可否確認4名蒙面人士為警務人員；警員反問為何查詢，又指自己「不清楚」，然後關上鐵閘。記者今早觀察到，有一輛裝甲車、一輛水炮車、數架警車和小型旅遊巴士駛入政總。政總外圍封起多層水馬，所有出入口鎖上鐵閘，不准傳媒進出。<br />\n<br />\n2019-09-29 11:18:43<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483159-20190929.htm\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483159-20190929.htm&d=kT0D7NwRktyFNYuHQ%2Fv%2Be5ggdM0W6%2BkgeusliPwa7Y4%3D&h=214dbd3f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1483159-20190929.htm&h=3edfad97\" target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1483159-20190929.htm</a>"},{"pid":"cbf580d26cbb7711fc814ccecf38ef13ec5f8084","tid":1601273,"uid":212626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:46:01.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/scare.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"14188237203e2dbf09d0449d935a52950d52b910","tid":1601273,"uid":180168,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:48:54.000Z","msg":"今日如果有衝突<br />\n你地預咗又有卧底捉人啦"},{"pid":"4981dde3628e945b0669e36818c3a2d910bcaea6","tid":1601273,"uid":81052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:49:56.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/chicken.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d5e1da3b2cc4234654ad5fd4eee3e1c572f990f","tid":1601273,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-09-29T03:51:49.000Z","msg":"見到有衝突即刻走 等佢哋自己玩